WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.540 --> 00:00:03.660
As an Indie game developer you’ve been there.

00:00:04.060 --> 00:00:08.880
Those sleepless nights. Those programming glitches.

00:00:09.220 --> 00:00:13.240
It seems like your first big hit game is sooo far away.

00:00:13.460 --> 00:00:16.760
You have heard about the legend of Indie Games Accelerator:

00:00:17.260 --> 00:00:21.960
...a program by Google Play through which Indie Developers bring their ideas to life..

00:00:21.960 --> 00:00:25.760
...and build epic games and great adventures that people will love.

00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:30.380
Selected participants are flown to Google Asia's headquarter in Singapore...

00:00:30.660 --> 00:00:34.980
...where they receive direct coaching from the best mobile gaming experts in the world, ...

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:41.820
...and some game-changing rewards like Google Pixel phones, Google Cloud credits, and exclusive events invites!

00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:44.580
Missed your chance last time?

00:00:44.780 --> 00:00:49.760
Well, start your engines, cause a brand new adventure is about to begin!

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:54.500
Applications to the 2019 class of Indie Games Accelerator are now open...

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:59.320
...and this is your opportunity to supercharge your business on Google Play.

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:03.140
We are now welcoming passionate game developers from select countries...

00:01:03.140 --> 00:01:11.220
...in Latin America, Africa, Middle East and Asia - who are looking to supercharge their game….

00:01:11.220 --> 00:01:13.260
...and reach new heights.

00:01:13.260 --> 00:01:18.000
Apply for the program today, and give your game the next level-up!

